gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 130, Jazz 114
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Utah Jazz, 130-114. Harrison Barnes led the Kings with 33 points (11-16 FG, 5-7 3PT FG) and four rebounds as Domantas Sabonis added 22 points, 12 rebounds, and five assists. De'Aaron Fox added 18 points, six assists, and five rebounds for Sacramento. Jordan Clarkson led the Jazz with 24 points, six assists, and four rebounds as Lauri Markkanen totaled 19 points and 10 rebounds.
